---
title: In-App-Purchase Shame
---

<!-- Add your site or application content here -->
<%- first_game, *other_games = *GameRepository.read_top_100.compact %>
<div class='jumbotron'>
  <div class='row'>
    <div class='col-md-6'>
      <%- game = GamePresenter.new(first_game) %>
      <%= partial :game, locals: { game: game } %>
    </div>
    <div class='col-md-6'>
      <h3 class='text-center'>Shame On You</h3>
      <p>Looks like <em><%= game.title %></em> has the most shameful In-App Purchase recently posted to the App Store.
      Can you believe it? Who would want <em><%= game.top_iap_title %></em> anyway?
      Who is willing to pay <strong>$<%= game.top_iap_price %></strong> for it?</p>
      <p>Demand respect. Reject ludomania.</p>
      <p class='text-center'>The tyranny of the <strong><%= game.top_iap_title %></strong> must end.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<ul class='game-grid'>
  <%- other_games[1..4].map{|g| GamePresenter.new(g)}.each.with_index do |game, index| %>
    <li>
      <%= partial(:game, locals: { game: game }) %>
    </li>
  <%- end %>
</ul>
